00:29:49.492 --> 00:29:51.325
just because the breadth,
and the highlight,

00:29:51.325 --> 00:29:53.560
and the attention
hasn't been put there.

00:29:53.560 --> 00:29:56.910
And I would hope in
Central, South American

00:29:56.910 --> 00:29:58.840
and these Eastern
European countries,

00:29:58.840 --> 00:30:04.635
they're seeing the pervasiveness
of these different models.

00:30:04.635 --> 00:30:07.260
And there's no way that they're
not thinking about these things

00:30:07.260 --> 00:30:11.370
or adapting their models
to these sort of things.

00:30:11.370 --> 00:30:13.350
AUDIENCE: I was at the
