00:30:15.690 --> 00:30:19.170
were saying that they had found
that some of the advances that

00:30:19.170 --> 00:30:20.940
were just being noticed
in North America

00:30:20.940 --> 00:30:23.580
had been made in Russia
like a decade ago.

00:30:23.580 --> 00:30:25.800
And they had just
never transferred

00:30:25.800 --> 00:30:27.960
to the international
scholastic community

00:30:27.960 --> 00:30:30.150
because they were
Russian-centric.

00:30:30.150 --> 00:30:33.600
And I thought the that was a
