00:30:33.600 --> 00:30:36.780
about knowledge transfer, as
well as knowledge sharing.

00:30:36.780 --> 00:30:39.300
Because if our focus
is only on competing

00:30:39.300 --> 00:30:43.348
with East Asian countries
and Germany, to what extent

00:30:43.348 --> 00:30:45.390
are we missing opportunities
in the United States

00:30:45.390 --> 00:30:49.020
by paying attention to
