of the innovation frontier

00:39:22.350 --> 00:39:24.840
at that time, they really
went through this process

00:39:24.840 --> 00:39:28.500
of imitating what was out
there, and then from that basis,

00:39:28.500 --> 00:39:32.340
going on to innovate,
and do their own R&D,

00:39:32.340 --> 00:39:35.610
and create more advancements
for those products.

00:39:35.610 --> 00:39:39.570
And this trend really supported
by those close intertwined

00:39:39.570 --> 00:39:42.000
partnerships and
almost interdependence

00:39:42.000 --> 00:39:45.780
between the government
and the chebols.

