00:46:49.228 --> 00:46:50.605
let me just do one chart.

00:46:53.820 --> 00:46:57.270
Just so what recessions
look like in the US

00:46:57.270 --> 00:46:59.850
and what's been going on
and repeated sequences

00:46:59.850 --> 00:47:03.620
of recession, here's
the 1981 recession--

00:47:03.620 --> 00:47:06.510
dip, rise.

